343
00:28:46.820 --> 00:28:47.820
Baiklah.

344
00:28:48.159 --> 00:28:51.429
Ayo! Ayo singkirkan mereka.

345
00:28:58.199 --> 00:28:59.199
Bertahanlah di posisi itu

346
00:29:02.169 --> 00:29:03.199
